Usage: SET STATUS_REVERSE [ON|OFF|TOGGLE]
  When ON, client will display the status bar in reverse
  which is useful for black on white displays. This option
  only makes sense if your status bar is black and white
  only.

See Also:
  SET STATUS_FORMAT
